| No pagination on listing endpoints | **Medium** | Include in pre-close remediation checklist |
| No rate limiting or abuse prevention | **Medium** | Verify presence at infrastructure/gateway layer; if absent, require remediation |
| Hardcoded test data in production source | **Medium** | Code hygiene audit; indicator of code review process quality |
| README documents aspirational rather than actual state | **Medium** | Documentation accuracy audit; assess as indicator of engineering process maturity |
